03:03.033 --> 03:04.500
That's all.

03:04.567 --> 03:06.233
[gate buzzes]
- Count!

03:06.300 --> 03:08.934
[indistinct chatter]

03:09.000 --> 03:10.834
[gate buzzes]

03:10.900 --> 03:12.934
- It's got to be
in here somewhere.

03:19.433 --> 03:21.400
- What's going on?

03:21.467 --> 03:23.066
- Where is it?
- Where's what?

03:23.133 --> 03:24.567
- Hey, don't play games
with me, asshole.

03:24.633 --> 03:25.700
Where's the tunnel?

03:25.767 --> 03:27.734
- What tunnel?

03:27.800 --> 03:29.266
♪ ♪

03:29.333 --> 03:31.300
