of the prison wall.

03:52.133 --> 03:54.100
- When you go,
we're going with you.

03:54.166 --> 03:55.367
- How?

03:55.433 --> 03:56.967
We're gonna
leave at night.

03:57.033 --> 03:58.700
You'll be locked
into your own pod.

03:58.767 --> 04:01.033
- Then we'll switch pods.
- What?

04:01.100 --> 04:02.867
- You two will
switch pods with us.

04:02.934 --> 04:04.834
Otherwise, we tell the hacks
about what's going on.

04:04.900 --> 04:06.266
- All right.

04:06.333 --> 04:08.967
If you can arrange the exchange,
the tunnel's yours.

04:09.033 --> 04:11.600
- Rebadow!
- Shut up, Busmalis.

04:11.667 --> 04:14.767
- Yeah, shut up,
Bushman.

04:18.934 --> 04:21.967
- I can't let those Nazis
go through Lizzie.

04:22.033 --> 04:24.000
It would be like
they were raping her.

04:24.066 --> 04:26.667
- In my years at Oz,
I've learned one rule--

04:26.734 --> 04:28.900
accept the hand
you're dealt.

04:28.967 --> 04:30.734
We'll lose the
tunnel either way.

04:30.800 --> 04:33.333
Better to let it go and start
a new one in the next pod.

04:37.467 --> 04:40.266
- [sighs]
Oh, fuck.

04:40.333 --> 04:42.233
- Metzger?

04:42.300 --> 04:44.233
- Yeah?

04:46.233 --> 04:48.266
- I need an ask.

04:53.367 --> 04:54.834
- Hey, Tim,

04:54.900 --> 04:58.567
