05:22.967 --> 05:25.533
- Stupid fucks.

05:25.600 --> 05:28.633
[bell ringing]

05:41.800 --> 05:43.533
- There they go.

05:44.934 --> 05:47.600
How can you be so calm?

05:47.667 --> 05:49.834
