06:01.467 --> 06:03.233
Oh, shit.

06:03.300 --> 06:06.233
♪ ♪

06:06.300 --> 06:10.600
[grunts]

06:10.667 --> 06:13.300
Let's go, pussy.

06:16.433 --> 06:18.567
- They should
almost be there.

06:18.633 --> 06:19.633
- Yes.

06:19.700 --> 06:21.834
- We should've
told them.

06:21.900 --> 06:23.300
- No.

06:23.367 --> 06:24.500
- Yes.

06:24.567 --> 06:26.266
We should have
warned them

06:26.333 --> 06:28.500
that we weakened
all the support beams.

06:28.567 --> 06:30.166
We should have
warned them

06:30.233 --> 06:32.533
that the tunnel will collapse
on top of them.

06:32.600 --> 06:36.166
♪ ♪

06:36.233 --> 06:37.967
- Oh, shit.

06:38.033 --> 06:40.533
This fucking thing here.

06:40.600 --> 06:43.900
I think I can get by.

06:43.967 --> 06:45.734
♪ ♪

06:45.800 --> 06:47.567
Careful.

06:47.633 --> 06:49.467
[grunts]

06:49.533 --> 06:51.900
Oh, sh--
[rumbling]

06:51.967 --> 06:54.033
You all right?

06:54.100 --> 06:55.633
- Yeah.

07:03.033 --> 07:04.266
- Yeah!

07:04.333 --> 07:06.133
- What the hell
are you doing here?

07:06.200 --> 07:09.500
- Prisoner number 96N542,
Mark Mack.

07:09.567 --> 07:11.667
Convicted June 1, '96,

07:11.734 --> 07:15.633
murder in the second degree,
vandalism, hate crimes.

07:15.700 --> 07:18.033
Sentence--70 years.

07:18.100 --> 07:20.967
Up for parole in 40.
[bird caws]

07:21.033 --> 07:22.433
[rumbling]

07:22.500 --> 07:24.533
- Yo, back up!

07:24.600 --> 07:26.200
Back up, man!
Back up!

07:26.266 --> 07:27.667
Back up!
It's falling down.

07:27.734 --> 07:28.900
It's collapsing, man!

07:28.967 --> 07:30.867
Shit, man,
back up.

07:30.934 --> 07:32.033
Go, man, go!

07:34.934 --> 07:37.967
[both screaming]

07:44.033 --> 07:45.700
- I've been here
five minutes!

07:45.767 --> 07:47.667
I got two bodies
on my floor!

07:47.734 --> 07:51.333
This is not the way shit's
gonna happen with me here!

07:51.400 --> 07:53.700
We find one more hole,
who's going in it?

07:53.767 --> 07:55.734
I'm putting one
of you goddamn cocksuckers

07:55.800 --> 07:57.967
in the next fucking
hole we find!

07:58.033 --> 07:59.800
Who wants a shovel, huh?

07:59.867 --> 08:01.800
Dig me the goddamn hole!

08:01.867 --> 08:04.600
You gonna dig me a hole?
Go ahead!

08:05.934 --> 08:08.233
God damn it!

08:08.300 --> 08:11.133
- The tunnel was found in
what used to be your pod.

08:11.200 --> 08:13.700
- Yes, he dug it.

08:13.767 --> 08:15.266
- Rebadow.

08:15.333 --> 08:17.333
- Under orders
from Mark Mack.

08:17.400 --> 08:19.100
- Mack forced you to dig?

08:19.166 --> 08:22.266
- He threatened to kill
Busmalis, didn't he?

08:23.367 --> 08:26.500
- Yes,
the Nazi bastard.

08:26.567 --> 08:30.200
- If that's true,
you should have come to us.

08:30.266 --> 08:32.266
- That's easy to say.

08:32.333 --> 08:34.700
The poor man was terrified.

08:34.767 --> 08:36.633
- Terrified.

08:36.700 --> 08:38.700
- Busmalis warned
them of the dangers,

08:38.767 --> 08:41.800
but they were
so anxious to go.

08:41.867 --> 08:43.200
- They wouldn't
listen to a word.

08:43.266 --> 08:46.367
- Um, even so...

08:46.433 --> 08:48.000
these two
should be punished.

08:48.066 --> 08:51.233
- Well, neither one has much
of a discipline problem.

08:52.767 --> 08:54.700
You can go.

08:56.700 --> 09:00.066
[gate buzzes in the distance]

09:00.133 --> 09:03.066
[tense percussive tones]

09:03.133 --> 09:06.433
[indistinct chatter]

09:06.500 --> 09:13.533
♪ ♪

09:18.900 --> 09:21.266
