don't deserve to be laws.

17:25.800 --> 17:27.867
But you,

17:27.934 --> 17:29.367
you, you...

17:29.433 --> 17:32.567
fucking baby raper,
you should be dead.

17:32.633 --> 17:35.367
- Back in your cage,
Schillinger.

17:35.433 --> 17:36.867
Don't make
me use this.

17:36.934 --> 17:39.066
You wouldn't want me to
enjoy myself, now, would you?

17:39.133 --> 17:42.333
[laughter, indistinct chatter]

17:47.233 --> 17:48.934
- Way to go, Vern!

17:49.000 --> 17:52.266
[laughter]

17:52.333 --> 17:53.867
